Project description

AWS Lambda Typing

A package that provides type hints for AWS Lambda event, context and responseobjects. It's a convenient way to get autocomplete and type hints built intoIDEs. Type annotations are not checked at runtime but are only enforced by thirdparty tools such as type checkers, IDEs, linters, etc.

Usage

Example: AWS SQS event

from aws_lambda_typing import context as context_, eventsdef handler(event: events.SQSEvent, context: context_.Context) -> None:    for record in event['Records']:        print(record['body'])    print(context.get_remaining_time_in_millis())    message: events.sqs.SQSMessage
